'''GoFundMe'''是美国一个营利性[[群眾募資|众筹]]平台，人们可以在這個平台上筹集资金<ref name="Bloomberg">{{Cite web|title=Moneymaking Ideas|url=http://images.businessweek.com/slideshows/20120131/moneymaking-ideas/slides/2|accessdate=June 16, 2012|work=Bloomberg Businessweek|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120624231030/http://images.businessweek.com/slideshows/20120131/moneymaking-ideas/slides/2|archivedate=June 24, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=How to fundraise|url=http://www.gofundme.com/how-to-fundraise/|accessdate=April 30, 2012|publisher=GoFundMe|archive-date=2012-05-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120501045742/http://www.gofundme.com/how-to-fundraise}}</ref>。从2010年到2020年初，人們在该平台上共筹集了超过90亿美元的资金，有超过1.2亿名捐赠者向該平台的集資者捐款<ref>{{Cite web|title=When GoFundMe Gets Ugly|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2019/11/gofundme-nation/598369/|accessdate=1 December 2019|date=1 November 2019|archive-date=2021-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210514100746/https://www.theatlantic.com/magazine/archive/2019/11/gofundme-nation/598369/}}</ref>。GoFundMe总部位于美國加利福尼亞州[[紅木城|紅木城]]<ref name="gofundme.com">{{Cite web|title=Why GoFundMe: Most Trusted Free Fundraising Platform|url=https://www.gofundme.com/why-gofundme|accessdate=2018-03-13|publisher=GoFundMe|language=en|archive-date=2018-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180314043246/https://www.gofundme.com/why-gofundme}}</ref>。

2015年7月2日，GoFundMe, Inc.完成 Accel Partners 和 TCV 領投，[[格雷洛克合伙公司|格雷洛克合伙公司]]、Meritech Capital Partners、ICONIQ Capital等跟投的A輪融資，金額不詳<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.mg21.com/gofundme.html |title=全球最大筹款平台：GoFundMe, Inc. |publisher=美股之家 |date=2021-06-02 |access-date=2021-06-02 |archive-date=2021-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210604082327/https://www.mg21.com/gofundme.html }}</ref>。

